#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.rad2deg.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.rad2deg"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg:1 of
msgid "Convert angles from radians to degrees."
msgstr "将角度从弧度转换为度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg:3 of
msgid "Angle in radians."
msgstr "以弧度表示的角度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg:5 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供，其形状必须可以广播到输入的形状。如果未提供"
"或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）的长度必须"
"等于输出的数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg:10 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg:15 of
msgid "**y** -- The corresponding angle in degrees."
msgstr "**y** -- 对应的以度为单位的角度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg:20 of
msgid ":py:obj:`deg2rad`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg:21 of
msgid "Convert angles from degrees to radians."
msgstr "将角度从度转换为弧度。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg:24 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg:25 of
msgid "rad2deg(x) is ``180 * x / pi``."
msgstr "rad2deg(x) 等价于 ``180 * x / pi``。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.rad2deg.rad2deg:28 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

